pageTitle: jQTree4PHP: Generate expansible tree menus using Jquery - PHP Classes
textBeforeTable: Omar Yepez This package can be used to generate expansible tree menus. It generates HTML and Javascript that use the Jquery library to present an hierarchical menu of tree nodes that can expand and collapse. The tree items are rendered as lists with configurable icons and actions to be associated when the user clicks on the items.     Author   Description HTML, PHP 5 5.0 GNU General Publi... jqtree4php 1.0.0     Categories   PHP version   Licenses   Version
